(2, 1, '2018-03-26 21:37:25', '2018-03-26 21:37:25', '&nbsp;\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.2 !important;\">\r\n<h3 align=\"center\"><b><big><big>Delivery and Refund Policy</big></big></b></h3>\r\n&nbsp; \r\n&nbsp; \r\nWelcome to <b>Jzubes</b> and thank you for considering to purchase with us.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1><big><b>Our Delivery Policy</b></big></h1>\r\n&nbsp; \r\nSingle and packaged digital products purchased from <b>Jzubes</b> will be available for download as soon as the purchase is successfully completed. Please visit &nbsp;<b><a href=\"/account\">My Account</a></b> and log-in to download your purchased product(s).\r\n&nbsp; \r\nDomain names are digitally delivered within <b>24 hours</b> of your completed purchase. Please check the email address you provided (even your spam folder) for details on how to access your domain account.\r\n&nbsp; \r\nWebsites will be digitally delivered within <b>48 hours</b> of your completed purchase. Please check the email address you provided for details to access your purchased website.\r\n&nbsp; \r\n&nbsp; \r\n<h1><big><b>Our Refund Policy</b></big></h1>\r\n&nbsp; \r\n<b>Refund requests must be submitted within 30 days of the product delivery date.</b>\r\n&nbsp; \r\n<b>Single and Business Package Product Refunds</b> \r\nSingle and Business Package product purchases are eligible for a complete, no quibble refund, excluding:\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pre-Built Website Package (EWB01)</li>\r\n 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;Domain name purchases</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIndividually purchased <b>Jzubes</b> products are eligible for a 100% no quibble refund of the cost of the item when the customer submits a refund request.\r\n&nbsp; \r\n<b>Pre-Built Website Package Product (EWB01) Refunds</b>\r\nWebsite Package product purchases are eligible for a 50% no quibble refund of the invoiced cost of the item, non-negotiable. Digital website building requires additional charges and labor on behalf of <b>Jzubes</b>, and this portion of the work cannot be refunded or returned.\r\n&nbsp; \r\n<b>Domain Name Refunds</b>\r\nDomain name purchases are not eligible for a refund, as domain registration fees are passed on to a naming authority that do not repossess or repeal names that have been allocated. If the domain name was purchased as part of a bundle or as part of the Web Business Package, the customer can request a refund on the other digital items included in the package. Non-eligibility applies to purchased domain names only.\r\n&nbsp; \r\n&nbsp; \r\n<h1><big><b>Our Refund Terms and Conditions</b></big></h1>\r\n&nbsp; \r\n<b>Refund requests must be submitted within 30 days of the product delivery date.</b>\r\n&nbsp; \r\nIf a refund is requested on the Pre-Built Website Package Product EWB01, access to the website, its content and folder structure will be revoked immediately.  All the content will subsequently be deleted when the refund has been completed.\r\n&nbsp; \r\nAs domain names are non-refundable, customers retain ownership of their domain name(s). A domain name can remain with our hosting provider or be transferred at a cost to another.\r\n&nbsp; \r\nAny refund requests submitted more than 30 days after delivery will be denied.  Furthermore, where a customer has received a refund on a past purchase with <b>Jzubes</b>, they will <b>not be eligible for another refund.</b>  In other words, subsequent or future purchases after a successful refund will not qualify for a full or partial refund.\r\n&nbsp; \r\n&nbsp; \r\n<b>How to Request a Refund</b>\r\n&nbsp; \r\n<b><u>Email Support:</u></b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Send us a message to <a href=\"mailto:Support@jzubes.com\"><b>Support@jzubes.com</b></a>, or\r\n&nbsp; \r\n<b><u>Contact Us Page:</u></b>&nbsp;&nbsp;In the menu above, click <a href=\"./../contact-us/\"><b>Contact Us</b></a> to send us a message via our contact form, and we will respond as quickly as possible. \r\n&nbsp;\r\nTell us the email address used for the purchase, the invoice or purchase confirmation number, and the portion of the invoice you would like refunded.\r\n&nbsp; \r\nPlease include the reason you are requesting a refund on your invoice. Though a reason is not required to fulfil your refund request, our <b>Jzubes</b> team would love to hear from you. Your feedback helps us make our products and our business practice better for all customers.\r\n&nbsp; \r\n&nbsp; \r\n\r\n&nbsp; \r\n<h2>Licensing</h2>\r\nYour license will run for 12 months and entitles you to free support and updates through that period. After a year, we’ll send you a reminder to renew your license at a 50% discount. If you don’t wish to renew, you can continue to use the product but support and updates will no longer be available.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Deliveries and Refunds', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'delivery-and-refunds', '', '', '2019-10-31 19:56:58', '2019-10-31 18:56:58', '', 0, 'http://jzubes.com/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
