(895, 1, '2019-08-10 14:13:03', '2019-08-10 13:13:03', '<div id=\"align_to_page\" class=\"clearfix\">\r\n<div id=\"u39157\" class=\"blowoutnumcolor clearfix colelem\">\r\n\r\n<!-- group -->\r\n<div id=\"u39158-4\" class=\"clearfix grpelem\">\r\n\r\n<!-- content -->\r\n<p class=\"blowoutnumber\">Section #03</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"u39161\" class=\"prodheader clearfix colelem\">\r\n\r\n<!-- group -->\r\n<div id=\"u39165-4\" class=\"prodhead clearfix grpelem\">\r\n\r\n<!-- content -->\r\n<h1>Health and Wellness Package</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"u39160\" class=\"prodboxgry rounded-corners clearfix colelem\">\r\n\r\n<!-- column -->\r\n<div id=\"ummhack39168\" class=\"size_fixed xcolelem\" data-sizepolicy=\"fixed\" data-pintopage=\"page_fixedLeft\">\r\n\r\n<!-- custom html -->\r\n\r\n<img class=\"lazy\" style=\"display: inline;\" src=\"http://jzubes.com/wp-content/uploads/Health-Wellness-Pkg.png\" data-original=\"http://jzubes.com/wp-content/uploads/Health-Wellness-Pkg.png\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"u39164-4\" class=\"clearfix colelem\">\r\n\r\n<!-- content -->\r\n<p class=\"proddesc\">What would <i>you</i> gain from our Health &amp; Wellness Package?</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"u39162-24\" class=\"clearfix colelem\">\r\n\r\n<!-- content -->\r\n<p class=\"prodbody1\">Our Health &amp; Wellness Package is just what you need to kickstart your brand-new wellness business, draw traffic to your website, gain leads for your email list, and, of course, inform your customers about health &amp; wellness.</p>\r\n<p class=\"prodbody1\">With titles like, “How Yoga will Strengthen Your Immune System”, “Healthy Lifestyle Practices for a Strong Heart”, and “Accidental Brain Training”, this package covers a ton of ground in the industry. Our variety of unique, varying content centered on health &amp; wellness will attract consumers, generate leads, and ultimately boost clicks and revenue on your website.</p>\r\n<p class=\"prodbody1\">Because let’s face