ell Sales Videos, OTO Sales Funnel Pages</li>\r\n  <li class=\"\">Autoresponder Email Swipes</li>\r\n  <li class=\"\">Resource Cheat Sheets</li>\r\n  <li class=\"\">Keyword Reports</li>\r\n  <li class=\"\">Articles In Multiple Formats</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"u39260-37\" class=\"bullet16 clearfix grpelem\">\r\n\r\n<!-- content -->\r\n<ul id=\"u39260-35\" class=\"list0 bbwyg\">\r\n  <li class=\"\">Amazon Product Review &amp; Banners</li>\r\n  <li class=\"\">Social Media Image Pack &amp; Update Posts</li>\r\n  <li class=\"\">Mindmap For Visual Learners</li>\r\n  <li class=\"\">Educational Infographics</li>\r\n  <li class=\"\">MP4, MOV, WMV, Full HD Video Formats For Editing And Re-branding Videos.</li>\r\n  <li class=\"\">Web Ready Videos in Multiple Formats - Just Upload And View</li>\r\n  <li class=\"\">Video Transcripts</li>\r\n  <li class=\"\">High Quality MP3 Audio &amp; Editable WAV Audios</li>\r\n  <li class=\"\">Transparent PNGs &amp; JPGs For The Ecovers And Graphic Elements.</li>\r\n  <li class=\"\">Running Time: Over 19 Hours</li>\r\n  <li class=\"\">Product Size: Over 52 GB</li>\r\n  <li class=\"\">Master Resell Rights</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Preview alinks - div -->\r\n<div id=\"u26531-4\" class=\"clearfix grpelem\">\r\n<div class=\"showset\"><a id=\"buttonu51147\" class=\"nonblock nontext Button smallbutton clearfix colelem view-package\" style=\"color: white; text-align: center;\" href=\"/eShop/PTitle/PTitle-FE/Silver Web/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Preview Sales Page</a>\r\n<a id=\"buttonu51147\" class=\"nonblock nontext Button smallbutton clearfix colelem view-package\" style=\"color: white; text-align: center;\" href=\"/eShop/PTitle/PTitle-UPS/Gold Web/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Preview One-Time-Offer Page</a>\r\n<a id=\"buttonu51147\" class=\"nonblock nontext Button smallbutton clearfix colelem view-package\" style=\"color: white; text-align: center;\" href=\"/eShop/PTitle/PTit