(774, 1, '2019-04-16 23:33:56', '2019-04-16 22:33:56', '<div class=\"clearfix\" id=\"align_to_page\"> <div class=\"blowoutnumcolor clearfix colelem\" id=\"u83657\"><!-- group -->\r\n        <div class=\"clearfix grpelem\" id=\"u83658-4\"><!-- content -->\r\n         <p class=\"blowoutnumber\">Product #67</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n       </div>\r\n       <div class=\"prodheader clearfix colelem\" id=\"u83660\"><!-- group -->\r\n        <div class=\"prodhead clearfix grpelem\" id=\"u83664-4\"><!-- content -->\r\n         <h1>Pinterest Marketing</h1>\r\n        </div>\r\n       </div>\r\n       <div class=\"prodboxgry rounded-corners clearfix colelem\" id=\"u83659\"><!-- column -->\r\n        <div class=\"size_fixed colelem\" id=\"ummhack83734\" data-sizepolicy=\"fixed\" data-pintopage=\"page_fixedLeft\"><!-- custom html -->\r\n         \r\n<img class=\"lazy\" src=\"http://jzubes.com/wp-content/uploads/603-vm-pinterest-marketing-mac-front.png\" srcx=\"data:image/png;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\">\r\n\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"clearfix colelem\" id=\"u83663-4\"><!-- content -->\r\n         <p class=\"proddesc\">Are You Ready To Learn Pinterest Marketing From A Completely New And Exciting Perspective With Viking Pinterest Marketing?</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"clearfix colelem\" id=\"u83661-8\"><!-- content -->\r\n         <p class=\"prodbody1\">There are so many social media platforms to choose from, that most business owners focus their time and attention on one or two. When deciding which sites are the best to brand and market your business, you must not forget the visually engaging Pins and Boards found on Pinterest.</p>\r\n         <p class=\"prodbody1\">There are a few ways in which Pinterest varies and stands out from other social media sites. While you can \"follow\" users, and they can \"follow\" you, it\'s not about friends and followers.</p>\r\n         <p class=\"prodbody1\">Instead, it is a