idence to know you can reach your goals</li>\r\n          <li class=\"wyg\">How To develop a high level of self-esteem so you can endure the tough periods</li>\r\n          <li class=\"wyg\">Develop positive environments for you to maintain high self-esteem</li>\r\n          <li class=\"wyg\">How To overcome the fears that hold you back from success</li>\r\n          <li class=\"wyg\">How To see mistakes as learning opportunities, not as events to fear</li>\r\n          <li class=\"wyg\">Why action is essential to achieving your goals</li>\r\n          <li class=\"wyg\">How To develop a thirst for taking action continuously to achieve more of your goals</li>\r\n          <li class=\"wyg\">How positive thoughts can aid your efforts to reach your goals</li>\r\n          <li class=\"wyg\">How negative thoughts can actually aid you in reaching your goals</li>\r\n          <li class=\"wyg\">Why core values are vital to your inner self and your goals</li>\r\n          <li class=\"wyg\">And so much more...</li>\r\n         </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"clearfix colelem\" id=\"u60377-4\"><!-- content -->\r\n         <p class=\"prodsummary\">What You Get With This Product</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"clearfix colelem\" id=\"pu60424-39\"><!-- group -->\r\n         <div class=\"bullet16 clearfix grpelem\" id=\"u60424-39\"><!-- content -->\r\n          <ul class=\"list0 bbwyg\" id=\"u60424-37\">\r\n           <li class=\"wyg\">Animated Flipbook Format for maximum customer engagement - View on Windows, MAC, Kindle, iBook, Kobo, Nook, BeBook, PocketBook, And More.</li>\r\n           <li class=\"wyg\">Ebook Also Comes In Animated Web Ready Format - Just Upload, Point Your Browser, And View!</li>\r\n           <li class=\"wyg\">Multi-Format Ebook For Maximum Device Compatibility.</li>\r\n           <li class=\"wyg\">Ready Made Sales Website & Thank You Page</li>\r\n           <li class=\"wyg\">Ready Made Affiliate Pages</li>\r\n           <li clas